repository-code: "https://github.com/manishklach/ghostkv-lab"
url: "https://github.com/manishklach/ghostkv-lab"
abstract: >-
  GhostKV Lab is a research simulator for query-time bounded elimination of
  reconstructable KV-cache witnesses in long-context transformer inference.
  The repository focuses on synthetic evaluation of attention sketches,
  conservative elimination bounds, selective resurrection, and illustrative
  KV-memory movement modeling. Related to Indian provisional patent
  application 202641062451.
keywords:
  - ghostkv
  - kv-cache
  - llm-inference
  - long-context
  - transformer
  - systems-research
  - attention-optimization
  - memory-systems
